{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act34side_level_act34side_02_beg","storyGroup":"act34side","storySort":4,"storyDependence":"act34side_level_act34side_01_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"BP-2","storyName":"评议式迎接","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"艾丽妮跟随海巡队指挥官西昆妲调查数据员失踪的真相。歌蕾蒂娅就深海猎人的种种异常接受评议会的质询，众人齐聚斗智场，乌尔比安悄然出现在博士身侧。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act34side/level_act34side_02_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act34side_02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":2,"next":4,"characters":["西昆妲","海巡队队员","艾丽妮","西昆妲＆艾丽妮","乔迪","阿维图斯","“小帮手”","幽灵鲨","斯卡蒂","凯尔希","热情的阿戈尔人","疲惫的阿戈尔人","布兰都斯","阿戈尔女性","卡西娅","卢契拉","克莱门莎","？？？"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":1},{"type":"stopmusic","id":2},{"type":"dialog","id":3},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":8},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"这段时间，都没人进来过吗？","id":11},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":12},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"没有。","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"房间内小帮手的中控元件也确认过了，没有发现被篡改过的痕迹。","id":14},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"您好，请问这里这个记录要怎么查看？","id":16,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"给她打开权限。","id":18},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"是。","id":20},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#2$1","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"啊，谢谢你！","id":22,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/e/e8/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-2$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","focus":"n","id":23},{"type":"text","text":"西昆妲取下了腰间挂着的装置。她的笔尖飞舞，仿佛水藻般纠缠不清的线条不断地在装置的表面浮现。","id":24},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"你们的指挥官这是在？","id":26,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"写写画画有助于她快速思考，这是西昆妲的习惯，听说她还是研究员的时候就这样。","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"旁人理解不了，上面也没记什么关键词，全是一些只有她自己才能看懂的......呃，抽象画。","id":29},{"type":"dialog","id":30},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#3$1","id":31},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_penrustle","volume":"1","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（书籍按照薄厚的顺序排列，贝壳装饰物按照大小顺序摆放，从斗智场下载的所有资料则根据时间进行了归类。）","id":34},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（浮藻脂质霜剂，能有效防止皮肤干燥脱水，是因为弥利亚留姆要靠近海岸？）","id":35},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":36},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（这个分量，几乎够用三年。）","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（一名普通的阿戈尔女性。谨慎，甚至有些胆小和刻板，与发展规划所提供的资料相符。）","id":38},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"（那些微型水培箱——）","id":40},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"那些箱子是干什么用的？明明都空了，却还挂在墙上？","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#5$1","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"是的。水培箱应该是切入点。","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"对房间里所有与植物栽培相关的设备进行扫描。","id":45},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"是。","id":47},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"以及，从图利娅的档案里调取相关的信息，她或许有这方面的爱好。","id":49},{"type":"dialog","id":50},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_scan","volume":"1","id":51},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":52},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"图利娅曾就职于生态艺术创作所，主要负责濒危深海藻类的培育。","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"根据生态艺术创作所的资料......","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"经过艺术家的精心培育，这些深海藻类能够在生长的过程中相互交织，组成一幅不断反映着生命进程的、动态的画。","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"这些微型水培箱是图利娅的个人资产，这里有她当时的作品影像。","id":57},{"type":"dialog","id":58},{"type":"charslot","id":59},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#7$1","id":60},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#6$1","id":61},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲＆艾丽妮","text":"很漂亮。","id":63,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d9/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-6$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#9$1","id":64},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#3$1","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲＆艾丽妮","text":"......","id":66,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-3$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","id":67},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#1$1","id":68},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"但这些水培箱看起来已经空置了很长时间。","id":69,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/66/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"档案刚刚提到，图利娅是转岗后才加入的航道计划。","id":71},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"她是因为某些原因放弃了过去的生活吗？","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"嗯。她的失踪很可能与职业生涯的变故有关。","id":75},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"扫描结果怎么样？","id":76},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":77},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"各类植物栽培设备并无异常，但我们在房间的集成终端上发现了一份操作记录。","id":78},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"图利娅在失踪前两天，从信标塔中控室下载过一份数据，并在自己的房间内制作了一份备份。","id":79},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"但我们在房间内并没有发现它。","id":80},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"追踪她的行程，同时联系中控室，从他们那边的下载记录去追溯数据内容。","id":82},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4009_irene_1#7$1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾丽妮","text":"如果她在失踪前还能正常地在工作场所与住所之间往来，那她的同僚或亲友也许对她的行为有所了解？","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/39/Avg_avg_4009_irene_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4137_udflow_1#1$1","id":85},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"是的。","id":86},{"type":"dialogue","name":"西昆妲","text":"对主要社会关系的问询安排好了吗？报案人呢？","id":87},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1391_1#1$1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"海巡队队员","text":"已经安排妥当，很快就可以与她们会面。","id":89},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialog","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"charslot","id":93},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":94},{"type":"curtain","direction":"0","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.12","block":"false","id":95},{"type":"curtain","direction":"4","fillfrom":"0.01","fillto":"0.15","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","xScale":"1.2","yScale":"1.2","x":"60","id":97},{"type":"backgroundtween","duration":"40","xTo":"-60","block":"false","id":98},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":99},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$m_dia_street_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_dia_street_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":100,"musicid":1},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":101},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"......","id":102},{"type":"dialog","id":103},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":104},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"乔迪，有什么我能帮到你的吗？","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"抱歉，我脑袋里问题太多，有点不知道......","id":107},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"这棵......金属的“树”？我只要对它提问就好了吗？我小时候也听过古树保管知识的传说，但我从没见过这样的......","id":108},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"被你称作“树”的珊瑚状装置是一个巨型集成终端，它是阿戈尔千百年来知识与文化的沉淀。","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"我们的所想、所知、所作、所赏，乃至许多仍待解答的问题，都储存在这里。它构成了斗智场的核心。","id":110},{"type":"dialog","id":111},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"background","screenadapt":"coverall","id":113},{"type":"curtain","id":114},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":115},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":116},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","duration":"1","id":117},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":118},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":119},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"所以，斗智场究竟是......","id":121},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"最早由伟大的人类学家暨先史文明研究者玛利图斯提出创意并主持修建的公共设施，对整个国家都影响深远的伟大设计。","id":123},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"除了海面上互相支撑的环礁城市群和海沟下模块化的城市网络，我们的其他城市大多形态各异，很少有同质化的设计。","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"但许多城市都不约而同地采纳了玛利图斯的设计，设立了自己的斗智场。","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"看看周围的人，他们在此思考、质疑、辩论，最后取得理解，做出决定。","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"最复杂的公式，最古老的图纸，最优美的诗歌......还有最适合的道路，都在这里诞生。这正是玛利图斯希望看到的景象吧。","id":127},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您一直在提的玛利图斯......那是个怎样的人？","id":129},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":130},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"要细数他为阿戈尔做出的所有贡献，恐怕一整天的时间也不够用。不过除此之外，我倒是还了解一些他的性格特质。","id":131},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":132},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"您认得他？","id":133},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#3$1","focus":"r","id":134},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"没有没有，玛利图斯生活在两百多年前，早在我出生之前，他就已经从阿戈尔消失了。","id":135},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"不过，他的怪脾气是我们学科的导师们津津乐道的话题。玛利图斯的理论推演能力极为出众，却很不喜欢自己得出结论。","id":137},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"在别人看来已经确凿无疑的事情，他也还要与自己辩论良久，才愿意得出结论。","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"有人认为他是过分在意事物的价值与意义，才会陷入这无休止的辩论，但这不正是我们身为人类的天性？","id":139},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"正因如此，他才主持修建了斗智场。事实证明，我们确实需要一个随时能让我们与自己、与他人展开思辨的场所。","id":140},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":141},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"我没有什么可以用来辩论的观念，阿维图斯先生......但我确实还有很多问题。我是该问您，问我自己，还是问这台终端？","id":142},{"type":"dialog","id":143},{"type":"charslot","id":144},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_microrobot","volume":"0.6","id":145},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1401_1#1$1","duration":"0.4","id":146},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","posfrom":"-200,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":147},{"type":"delay","time":"1.3","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"“小帮手”","text":"——","id":149},{"type":"dialog","id":150},{"type":"charslot","id":151},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":152},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"看来，我们的小讨论得暂时让步于一场更大的交锋了。","id":154},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":155},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"怎么了？","id":156},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"这里接下来要进行一场重要的评议会，和你那三位同行者相关。","id":158},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"深海猎人？！","id":160},{"type":"dialog","id":161},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":162},{"type":"charslot","id":163},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_inside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":164},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.4","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":165},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":166},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":167},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","duration":"0.5","id":168},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"哎呀，我是不是看见了我们迷茫的陆地朋友？他在一脸紧张地为我们担心呢。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#7$1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"（招手）","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/78/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-7$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#5","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"隔得太远了，他很难注意到。","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"3","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"但已经有其他人朝这边看过来了。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/80/Avg_char_263_skadi_5.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"这场评议会引起了过多计划外的关注。","id":178,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"深海猎人原本就足够引人注目了，“死而复生”又让故事平添了许多波折......","id":180,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"不论我们意愿如何，“深海猎人”都已经是这个舞台上的主角了。","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"鲨鱼，这场评议会是我们最后的“检查”了吧？","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"实话说，我已经有些厌烦了。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":185},{"type":"charslot","id":186},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"188","text":"幽灵鲨，你的状态还好吗？"},"2":{"id":"188","text":"斯卡蒂，别着急。"},"3":{"id":"188","text":"这么大阵仗，就当欢迎仪式吧。"}},"values":[],"id":187},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2","3"],"id":188,"end":190},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"深海猎人需要保持低调。但是博士，你我也需要谨慎行事。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":191},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":192},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"194","text":"罗德岛的处境总是这么微妙。"}},"values":[],"id":193},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":194,"end":198},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"是。这一次，我们不仅是在两个国家之间斡旋，更是在海洋与陆地之间，在两种文明之间斡旋。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"接下来我会短暂地离开你们，为歌蕾蒂娅策应。会议结束后，我将正式与阿戈尔的执政官接触，以求海陆合作能够达成。","id":197,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"只是，这座城市和我们所面对的局势都还不明朗。身处关注的焦点，有些事情我很难放开手脚去做。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":199},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":200},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"202","text":"但很少有人会关注你带来的“小助理”。"},"2":{"id":"202","text":"所以应当由我来见机行事，对吧？"}},"values":[],"id":201},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":202,"end":204},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_003_kalts_1#1$1","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"凯尔希","text":"嗯。务必注意行事方式，我不希望在与执政官谈判的时候，需要临时更换任务目标。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_avg_003_kalts_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":205},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":206},{"type":"charslot","duration":"1","id":207},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":208},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#14$1","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"博士，凯尔希医生在有些话题上总是格外依赖修辞艺术，不是吗？","id":210,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a0/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-14$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"绕来绕去的，她不是一直都这样讲话？","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我们的医生呀，总是在考虑太多的东西，却不善于表达自己的关心。","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"博士，你是不是也觉得，阿戈尔更加直率的沟通方式，更方便我们互相了解？","id":215,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":216},{"type":"charslot","id":217},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"219","text":"同意。"},"2":{"id":"219","text":"凯尔希有她的考量。"}},"values":[],"id":218},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":219,"end":224},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"放心，我和鲨鱼可以保护好你。","id":221,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"说起来，二队长怎么还没来？","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"她应该会和克莱门莎执政官一起出现。毕竟，今天需要站在正中央的人，其实是她。","id":224,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":225},{"type":"charslot","id":226},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","id":227},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":228},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":229},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的阿戈尔人","text":"那个，请问，您是劳伦缇娜小姐吗？","id":231},{"type":"dialog","id":232},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":233},{"type":"charslot","id":234},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","id":235},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":236},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":237},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","id":238},{"type":"interlude","maskid":"group_interclude_vertical_common","size":"290,760","style":"0","switch":"true","offset":"250,0","channel":"3","tsfrom":"0,1","tsto":"1,1","tsduration":"0.5","id":239},{"type":"3","channel":"3","slot":"m","switch":"true","pfrom":"235,0","pto":"235,0","name":"avg_npc_1393_1#1$1","duration":"1","id":240},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":241},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":242},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"顾问，您果然在这里。","id":243},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"这批环境样本的检测结果已经出来了，需要您过目一下，判断是否需要临时补充一轮新的基因检测。","id":244},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":245},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":246},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"啊，抱歉......你发了消息，但我没有注意终端。","id":247},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":248},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"true","id":249},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"您似乎很关心深海猎人的这场评议会。","id":250},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"我记得您原来在深海猎人研究所工作过？","id":251},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":252},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"我倒宁愿不提那份工作。","id":254},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不过是的，我在那研究基因嵌合的方式，尝试为深海猎人找到更安全、更有效的改造方案。","id":255},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":256},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"true","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"您不喜欢深海猎人计划？","id":258},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":259},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":260},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"一个付出了惨痛的牺牲，却没取得什么像样成果的失败项目罢了，谈不上什么喜欢不喜欢。","id":261},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"不过歌蕾蒂娅她们还活着，这是最重要的。就算为了她们几个，我也得来。","id":263},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":264},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"true","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"疲惫的阿戈尔人","text":"你们关系很好？","id":266},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1381_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":267},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","switch":"false","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"布兰都斯","text":"哈哈。要是歌蕾蒂娅也这么觉得就好了。","id":269},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"charslot","id":272},{"type":"interlude","channel":"3","clear":"true","id":273},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","id":274},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":276},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":277},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":278},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","posfrom":"100,0","posto":"0,0","duration":"1","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":280},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿戈尔女性","text":"阿维图斯老师，我能坐您旁边吗？","id":282},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"当然了，卡西娅。小心些坐，你刚接受过胚胎分离手术，还需要恢复。","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"这位是来自伊比利亚的客人，乔迪。","id":285},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"谢谢。你好。","id":287},{"type":"charslot","id":288},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_npc_1380_1#2$1","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"乔迪","text":"啊，您，您好。","id":290},{"type":"charslot","id":291},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#4$1","focus":"r","id":292},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"阿维图斯老师，今天的参加者是不是太多了点？","id":294},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"三个月前设施管理所也因为城市单元骨架的改造进行过一次评议，但关联单位只有两个。","id":295},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":296},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"毕竟评议会是严格以解决问题为导向的，只有问题复杂到单一部门无法解决，才会让间接相关的部门也参与进来。","id":297},{"type":"charslot","slot":"r","name":"avg_npc_1387_1#5$1","focus":"r","id":298},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"可现在斗智场已经坐了快一半人，深海猎人的回归，真的会有这么大的影响吗？","id":299},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#2$1","focus":"l","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"一项经过近两百年的争论才实际启动的计划......它的理念几乎动摇了阿戈尔的根基，它的动向同样牵动着阿戈尔的命脉。","id":301},{"type":"charslot","slot":"l","name":"avg_npc_1386_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"况且，航道计划已经进行到了最关键的阶段，任何预期之外的情况都值得关注。","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"仅靠垂直上报注定无法得到周全的结论，克莱门莎执政官需要听取更多领域的专业判断。","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿维图斯","text":"不过，现场应该还有很多人是自发前来旁听的。在这个敏感的时间点上，三位猎人的回归，或许会让许多人感到不安。","id":305},{"type":"dialog","id":306},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":307},{"type":"charslot","id":308},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","id":309},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","id":310},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":311},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":312},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":313},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的阿戈尔人","text":"我和这场评议会没有直接的关系，只是听说您可能会出席......","id":314},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":315},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"你是？","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":317},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的阿戈尔人","text":"啊，抱歉。","id":318},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"热情的阿戈尔人","text":"我叫卢契拉，曾经和您的父母有过一面之缘！","id":320},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":321},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"标尺、墨水......你在这座城市的穹顶系统工作？","id":322,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":323},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我、我去年刚刚从那里调离，不过还在设施管理所，在地面负责城市单元骨架的检修和洋流测绘。","id":324},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#10$1","focus":"r","id":325},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"“不要去羡慕太阳，我们给予自身永恒的群星和无限的海洋。”","id":326,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/7b/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-10$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":327},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"很小的时候，公共养育所的抚养人带我们在这里进行过一次演出。","id":329},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#3$1","focus":"l","id":330},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我们设想将微型光学机械编制成矩阵，用光点的明暗变化，将人思考时的神经活动以美观的方式呈现出来。","id":331},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#4$1","focus":"l","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"大家排练了很久。但演出当天，斗智场罕见地出现了故障，整个场地一瞬间暗了下去，只有那些小机器闪着光。","id":333},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#1$1","focus":"l","id":334},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"当时观众里有对很般配的叔叔阿姨，他们变了个魔术——一条条光带凭空垂落在斗智场，穹顶伸出须腕，邀我们的小机器一同起舞。","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"一切是那么美轮美奂，场地的故障反而显得像是精心安排的......","id":336},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"我能想象那两个家伙得意的神情了。说不定，所谓的故障还真的应该算到他们头上。","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#8$1","focus":"l","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"等到发展规划所进行职业评估时，我几乎毫不犹豫地填报了穹顶系统。直到那时候我才知道，他们是很有名的穹顶设计师。","id":340},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"......后来我就没有再见过他们。","id":342},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#1$1","focus":"r","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"他们启发了你，一面之缘，恰如其分。","id":344,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f1/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-1$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":345},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"不过，你刚刚说自己变更了职务。既然你已经和我们头顶这透明的巨构结下了缘分，为什么......","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#9$1","focus":"l","id":347},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"我......","id":348},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":349},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卡西娅","text":"卢契拉！评议会快开始了，你要坐在这边吗？","id":350},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_4079_haini_1#5$1","focus":"l","id":351},{"type":"dialogue","name":"卢契拉","text":"抱歉，劳伦缇娜小姐，我的同事在叫我——欢迎回家，祝你们顺利。","id":352},{"type":"dialog","id":353},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"1","id":354},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","posfrom":"0,0","posto":"-200,0","duration":"1","afrom":"1","ato":"0","id":355},{"type":"delay","time":"2.5","id":356},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_1023_ghost2_1#12$1","focus":"r","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"幽灵鲨","text":"......","id":358,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a7/Avg_avg_1023_ghost2_1-12$1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"charslot","id":361},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":362},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":363},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":364},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":365},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"该来的人差不多都到齐了......","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png"},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#6","id":367},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"欸，博士，你要去哪？","id":368,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/8f/Avg_char_263_skadi_6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":369},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":370},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"372","text":"深海猎人太引人注目了。"},"2":{"id":"372","text":"只是不想被各种人盯着看，不用管我。"}},"values":[],"id":371},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":372,"end":374},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"char_263_skadi#3","id":373},{"type":"dialogue","name":"斯卡蒂","text":"好吧，你还真是听凯尔希的话。","id":374,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4c/Avg_char_263_skadi_3.png","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":375},{"type":"charslot","id":376},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":377},{"type":"dialog","id":378},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":379},{"type":"charslot","id":380},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.7","id":381},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_higheldshosfts","volume":"0.4","channel":"2","id":382},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":383},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.6","id":384,"musicid":2},{"type":"charslot","slot":"left","name":"avg_474_gladiia_1#1","duration":"1","id":385},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#2$1","duration":"1","id":386},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":387},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":388},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"相信各位已经知道，弥利亚留姆近日成功与伊比利亚方面建立联系。这意味着航道计划即将进入最为关键的阶段......","id":389},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":390},{"type":"text","text":"一缕光纹从庞大的珊瑚状终端脱离，环绕着克莱门莎，在空气中连接成轻盈的环，随着执政官的话语而舞动。","id":391},{"type":"text","text":"光纹交织成城市与浪潮、猎人与海嗣，言语被转化成可视的影像，声音在这一刻获得了纹理。","id":392},{"type":"text","text":"刚刚还在喧嚣的人群，转瞬间便安静下来。","id":393},{"type":"charslot","slot":"right","name":"avg_npc_1382_1#9$1","focus":"r","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"值此关键时刻，歌蕾蒂娅、斯卡蒂、劳伦缇娜，三位幸存的深海猎人顺利返回了阿戈尔。","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"她们的体检结果，以及歌蕾蒂娅提交的任务报告已经上传至斗智场的终端，相信诸位已经自行查阅过了。","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"就其中的种种异常状况......","id":397},{"type":"dialogue","name":"克莱门莎","text":"深海猎人总战争设计师之一，阿戈尔荣誉军团长，歌蕾蒂娅执政官将在此接受诸位的质询。","id":398},{"type":"dialog","id":399},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside","loop":"true","channel":"bgs","volume":"0","id":400},{"type":"soundvolume","volume":"0.6","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":401},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":402},{"type":"charslot","id":403},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","text":"","id":404},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":406},{"type":"text","text":"你越过几排阿戈尔人，找到一个相对靠后的位置，坐了下来。从这里看过去，斗智场中发生的一切尽收眼底，座位周围也没那么拥挤。","id":407},{"type":"text","text":"评议会已经开始，偌大的环形建筑，没有人高声说话，但每个人的发言都无比清晰。歌蕾蒂娅站在场中，所有人的目光都投注在她身上。","id":408},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2","id":409},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.5","text":"","id":410},{"type":"text","text":"很轻的脚步声，几不可闻。仿佛幽邃的穹顶在你身侧投下了一块阴影。","id":411},{"type":"dialog","id":412},{"type":"stopsound","channel":"bgs","fadetime":"2","id":413},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.4","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":414},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不要声张。","id":415},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"否则我会掐断你的喉咙。","id":416},{"type":"dialog","id":417},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","name":"avg_4145_Ulpia_1#1$1","duration":"1.5","bstart":"0.2","bend":"0.5","id":418},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":419},{"type":"charslot","slot":"m","focus":"n","id":420},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"422","text":"......"}},"values":[],"id":421},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":422,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":423},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":425},{"type":"image","id":426},{"type":"charslot","id":427}],"characters":["西昆妲","海巡队队员","艾丽妮","西昆妲＆艾丽妮","乔迪","阿维图斯","“小帮手”","幽灵鲨","斯卡蒂","凯尔希","热情的阿戈尔人","疲惫的阿戈尔人","布兰都斯","阿戈尔女性","卡西娅","卢契拉","克莱门莎","？？？"]}